%h1
  About The Language of Colour
  %span.small AIC Study Group

%h2 Scope
%p
  To share information, knowledge and expertise on studies and practices related to colour and language. To investigate the relationship of colour and language. To improve colour communication within and across languages. We welcome suggestions on activities that SGLC can engage with and support.

%h2 Chairman: Dimitris Mylonas
%p
  School of Electronic Engineering and Computer Science, Queen Mary University of London, UK
